name: Rewrite No Odoo
description: Rewrite Odoo-referencing code/text to Smarterp-neutral form
---
Rewrite the provided code or text to remove all Odoo-specific references and replace them with Smarterp-appropriate equivalents.

Rules:
1. Replace "Odoo" with "Smarterp" where referring to the platform/product
2. Replace `odoo` module imports with `smarterp` where appropriate
3. Replace Odoo-specific XML IDs with Smarterp conventions
4. Replace Odoo-specific terminology with neutral ERP terminology
5. Do NOT change generic programming terms (e.g., model, view, controller) unless they are Odoo-specific brand terms
6. Preserve all logic, formatting, and functionality
7. If something is genuinely ambiguous, state the assumption explicitly

Provide the rewritten text/code with a brief summary of changes made.
